enes.%20Every%20year%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20something%3A%20shocking%20mistakes%2C%20protests%2C%20statements%2C%20and%20speeches%2C%20some%20awkward%20encounters%2C%20or%20even%20a%20brawl%20or%20two.Over%20the%20years%2C%20some%20Oscar%20controversies%20hit%20on%20big%20issues%2C%20like%20Hollywood%E2%80%99s%20history%20with%20race%20and%20representation.%20Others%20are%20just%20plain%20weird%3A%20wrong%20winners%2C%20cringe%20moments%20that%20explode%20online%2C%20or%20that%20one%20time%20someone%20stormed%20the%20stage.%20And%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%20and%20the%20digital%20boom%2C%20these%20moments%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20disappear%3B%20they%20go%20viral%20and%20stick%20around%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Oscars%E2%80%99%20story%20forever.From%20Marlon%20Brando%20sending%20a%20protestor%20in%20his%20place%2C%20to%20the%20wild%20%E2%80%98Envelope-gate%E2%80%99%20blunder%20in%202017%2C%20to%20Will%20Smith%E2%80%99s%20headline-grabbing%20slap%20in%202022%20%E2%80%94%20these%20aren%E2%80%99t%20just%20blips.%20They%20show%20the%20Academy%20Awards%20night%20is%20more%20than%20just%20about%20movies%20and%20their%20recognition.%20The%20ceremony%20always%20ends%20up%20reflecting%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20real%20tensions%2C%20values%2C%20and%20flaws.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773577435000%2C%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129509158%2Cimgsize-51864.cms%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2F6-biggest-controversies-in-oscars-history-from-will-smiths-slap-to-envelope-gate-best-picture-mix-up%2Fphotostory%2F129509158.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20an%20American%20who%20studied%20at%20universities%20in%20China.%20The%20Chinese%20system%20was%20cheaper%20and%20set%20me%20up%20for%20success%20after%20graduation.%22%2C%22description%22%3A%22I%20studied%20in%20China%20twice%2C%20saving%20money%20on%20my%20education.%20I%20also%20found%20that%20Chinese%20education%20was%20